@base_url = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@username = admin
@password = 123456
@post_id = 1

### List Posts (paginated)
GET {{base_url}}/api/posts/?page=1&page_size=5

### Search + Ordering
GET {{base_url}}/api/posts/?search=python&ordering=-created_at

### Retrieve Post
GET {{base_url}}/api/posts/{{post_id}}/

### Create Post (Basic Auth via URL)
POST http://{{username}}:{{password}}@127.0.0.1:8000/api/posts/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "API Ready",
  "body": "created from VS Code REST Client"
}

### Update Post (PATCH)
PATCH http://{{username}}:{{password}}@127.0.0.1:8000/api/posts/{{post_id}}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "updated via PATCH"
}

### Replace Post (PUT)
PUT http://{{username}}:{{password}}@127.0.0.1:8000/api/posts/{{post_id}}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Replaced",
  "body": "replace body",
  "status": "DRAFT"
}

### Delete Post
DELETE http://{{username}}:{{password}}@127.0.0.1:8000/api/posts/{{post_id}}/
